# Push notifications

# <https://github.com/variadico/noti>

# Use:
noti -t "Title"noti -t "Title" -m "Message"

# Configuration:

# - `.noti.yaml`:
    ---    pushbullet:      accessToken: 1234567890abcdefg      deviceIden: 1234567890abcdefg

# - Envorinment variable:
    export NOTI_DEFAULT='pushbullet'

